 * JSON LSP Sidecar Service
 * 
 * Provides JSON language intelligence using vscode-json-language-server:
 * - Completions (from JSON schemas)
 * - Hover information (from schemas)
 * - Diagnostics (syntax errors, schema validation)
 * - Formatting
